<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Certificate of Completion</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #3498db;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #3498db;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .congratulations {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #27ae60;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .course-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
        }
        .course-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .certificate-number {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .download-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .download-btn:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }
        .verification {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #27ae60;
        }
        .verification-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #27ae60;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ecf0f1;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üéì EduSoma</div>
            <div class="title">Certificate of Completion</div>
            <div class="subtitle">Congratulations on your achievement!</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="congratulations">
                üéâ Congratulations, {{studentName}}!
            </div>

            <p>You have successfully completed the course and earned your certificate of completion. This is a significant achievement that demonstrates your dedication and hard work.</p>

            <div class="course-info">
                <div class="course-name">{{courseName}}</div>
                <div class="certificate-number">Certificate #: {{certificateNumber}}</div>
                <div class="certificate-number">Issued: {{completionDate}}</div>
            </div>

            <p>Your certificate is now available for download. This certificate serves as official recognition of your successful completion of the course.</p>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{certificateUrl}}" class="download-btn">
                    üìÑ Download Certificate
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="verification">
                <div class="verification-title">üîç Certificate Verification</div>
                <p>This certificate can be verified using the unique certificate number: <strong>{{certificateNumber}}</strong></p>
                <p>You can share this certificate with employers, add it to your professional portfolio, or include it in your resume.</p>
            </div>

            <p>We're proud of your accomplishment and hope this certificate opens new opportunities for your learning and career growth.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing EduSoma for your learning journey!</p>
            <p>If you have any questions about your certificate, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Website</a> |
                <a href="#">Support</a> |
                <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 